{"hba93cd59gbde3g4385gbc83g05e4b8c539b5": ["*The forest. Dark. Cold. Foreboding.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_AstarionHunger_SCO_Avatar_Dream.html", "2b0758d2-e1e8-909f-27dd-8feb4bb93335"], "h666c95c8g666cg470egbc35g939f95c2b7d5": ["Hello? Anyone there?", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_AstarionHunger_SCO_Avatar_Dream.html", "d999a244-4986-d6fd-a536-8ea3b45b0411"], "ha44a9842gffbbg4a06g997cgdd300c996e45": ["First, thou shalt not drink of the blood of thinking creatures.", "2f1880e6-1297-4ca3-a79c-9fabc7f179d3", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_AstarionHunger_SCO_Avatar_Dream.html", "5b5c8228-121d-c8be-f449-51a5328177bd"], "h90bdf395g599fg437cgb32dg8c04f0a2875c": ["Master? I was just coming to see you!", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_AstarionHunger_SCO_Avatar_Dream.html", "445ae906-9d72-3a44-6e29-a1be6e54e6f5"], "h22000349gd266g4092g9ce7ge5d102847b6e": ["Second, thou shalt obey me in all things.", "2f1880e6-1297-4ca3-a79c-9fabc7f179d3", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_AstarionHunger_SCO_Avatar_Dream.html", "93f0aff4-71e5-38bf-beaa-28752048dc6d"], "h9aae73e5gd50eg463dgad2fgfbbc5beff97e": ["Absolutely. It's just that I was kidnapped by a tentacle-faced -", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_AstarionHunger_SCO_Avatar_Dream.html", "91fa78dc-f550-f1ac-e3a0-ec4b67d8b6b0"], "h807add13gea83g4f97gb60eg416c193a38a8": ["Third, thou shalt not leave my side unless directed.", "2f1880e6-1297-4ca3-a79c-9fabc7f179d3", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_AstarionHunger_SCO_Avatar_Dream.html", "a072458a-f14c-38b2-8b5f-3f13c90c2d82"], "h87a4006cg155dg43ecg853fgbc7a3c1f1c7b": ["*You can feel the old fear turning in your gut, but you force yourself to keep smiling. As you so often did before.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_AstarionHunger_SCO_Avatar_Dream.html", "15574b6b-0923-cc03-1776-dfb9bb35bb28"], "hd29537c7g2902g41e4g94cfgf0c52cefe536": ["Fourth, thou shalt know that thou art <i>mine</i>.", "2f1880e6-1297-4ca3-a79c-9fabc7f179d3", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_AstarionHunger_SCO_Avatar_Dream.html", "b758c605-a2d6-6ef0-7d3c-5d887210bb98"], "h82db8328g05edg4762g900bge597746c96f9": ["Not anymore. I'm free now.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_AstarionHunger_SCO_Avatar_Dream.html", "4f5422f6-33cb-2c3b-d60e-8843e210ba98"], "h65c210e1g93c1g4d44ga4d2g6647e8e8b817": ["Free? Lie to yourself, boy, but not to me.", "2f1880e6-1297-4ca3-a79c-9fabc7f179d3", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_AstarionHunger_SCO_Avatar_Dream.html", "5b87b41c-55fc-77e8-ed33-23edf1bf3aa8"], "he5d4b2bbgb7a0g449fg8e0fg01bef9106347": ["You are mine. Forever.", "2f1880e6-1297-4ca3-a79c-9fabc7f179d3", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_AstarionHunger_SCO_Avatar_Dream.html", "2cdff7d9-2090-19ff-5da9-0a553580ef58"], "hfc7470deg74f3g40begb4b4gf7ca1cfd50de": ["Please, you have to forgive me.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_AstarionHunger_SCO_Avatar_Dream.html", "44d64142-e82c-7f7e-2f4e-245b127cbf39"], "h1a9eb5b0g79c5g4537g9ef2g3d0656f86922": ["Pathetic. As always. But at least you know your place.", "2f1880e6-1297-4ca3-a79c-9fabc7f179d3", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_AstarionHunger_SCO_Avatar_Dream.html", "1f4e0f8c-69ca-e8c3-6bc2-a48f8ed0df83"], "h64f2f7cagf57fg4643gb0f6g570ed9d97500": ["<i>Attack.</i>", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_AstarionHunger_SCO_Avatar_Dream.html", "9f04a047-dba2-618b-741b-757bc5e2fab9"], "h353c8e90g837fg45dega392g36b7eb16a095": ["*You swing, but connect with nothing. His twisted, smiling face remains.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_AstarionHunger_SCO_Avatar_Dream.html", "3e1801f3-9ca8-dd5b-aa30-8b0ef30eb36f"], "hf439e53ag6e53g4b0aga5cbgcb16abb2a27e": ["*Your heart pounds, but you're ready. He's going to regret coming for you.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_AstarionHunger_SCO_Avatar_Dream.html", "a30220ec-f52a-53ec-55e6-cefd7775d33d"], "h77ceafcbg8e4eg410fgb577gcda2ab4505d0": ["No. Please. Not again!", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_AstarionHunger_SCO_Avatar_Dream.html", "d62cb9a8-b03b-656a-3f39-f92d413a8dde"], "h88411be0g9502g40f2gab91g3f1da5be1f30": ["Where are you?  Show yourself!", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_AstarionHunger_SCO_Avatar_Dream.html", "1c976692-877c-eaba-85c6-a6cd03009a84"], "hc20d746bg1b8cg480bga892g6c45a611202b": ["*You keep low to the ground, scuttling like a rat.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_AstarionHunger_SCO_Avatar_Dream.html", "7f65e416-390d-3e47-6dc7-b9ff20a6462d"], "hddeab213ga5cbg4035g9112g68459e7bee36": ["Hello? Show yourself!", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_AstarionHunger_SCO_Avatar_Dream.html", "346c3501-fc59-1cb7-e5b2-f4bb777c3794"], "ha0508d30gf7a4g4a9ag9a48g98ef8ea45ae0": ["<i>Try to sneak away.</i>", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_AstarionHunger_SCO_Avatar_Dream.html", "e08af795-2f0b-bf74-b420-3b8d6c6708a0"]}